            . I live in <placeName id="t18310512-36-crimeloc231">Leather-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310512-36-crimeloc231" type="placeName" value="Leather-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310512-36-crimeloc231" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310512-36-off229 t18310512-36-crimeloc231"></join>, and am a tallow-chandler. On the 15th of April Mr. Jacques' cart called for a box of candles - I was packing them in my shop, and saw the prisoner shoulder a tub of butter from the cart - I immediately pursued him; on finding that, he threw the tub of butter into an empty cart, and ran on - I called a neighbour to take him; I stopped the cart, and took the butter out of it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310512-36-person365">
                  GEORGE 
                  BEAN
               <interp inst="t18310512-36-person365" type="surname" value="BEAN"></interp>
