                  </persName>
            . I had put the tub of butter into the cart, and then went to Mr. Green's - the tub was taken from the cart while I waited there; I did not see it taken, but I saw it afterwards, and knew it was the same which had been in the cart.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going by the witness' door, and when I had got forty of fifty yards he came and said I was the person he wanted.</p>
